00:14:43.880 --> 00:14:45.020
across the system.

00:14:45.020 --> 00:14:48.130
But we have stylised it.

00:14:48.130 --> 00:14:51.430
The entry chips for the
addressees in the middle

00:14:51.430 --> 00:14:52.780
of the screen here.

