00:15:38.300 --> 00:15:42.350
We've updated the weights, using
the guidance that comes out

00:15:42.350 --> 00:15:45.470
of the Material Theme Editor
to optimize how we want to size

00:15:45.470 --> 00:15:47.030
them as well.

00:15:47.030 --> 00:15:51.260
With the bold headlines and less
emphasized captions and body

00:15:51.260 --> 00:15:55.970
text, we increase the
scanability of the content.

00:15:55.970 --> 00:15:57.650
And you can see
that really clearly

00:15:57.650 --> 00:16:00.050
in a view like the
messaging list here.

00:16:00.050 --> 00:16:01.720
