You're getting a little bit of
that background color peeking

00:16:29.090 --> 00:16:31.670
through between the
cards, cuing that these

00:16:31.670 --> 00:16:34.460
are different surfaces and
that the user can reasonably

00:16:34.460 --> 00:16:38.360
expect they could perform swipe
gestures on it, in this case,

00:16:38.360 --> 00:16:41.690
to either star or delete
