00:16:55.670 --> 00:16:58.040
is that no matter what platform
you're building for, you have

00:16:58.040 --> 00:16:59.840
a consistent set of
components available,

00:16:59.840 --> 00:17:03.290
the same patterns, features,
theme ability, but still

00:17:03.290 --> 00:17:06.140
very much in line with
the platform specific

00:17:06.140 --> 00:17:09.641
paradigms that your users
are going to expect.

