So here on Android,
we have the same kind

00:17:11.349 --> 00:17:13.270
of material theming for color.

00:17:13.270 --> 00:17:16.390
We define our theme, inheriting
from the material components

00:17:16.390 --> 00:17:18.822
them, and define
our brand colors.

00:17:18.822 --> 00:17:20.280
This defines all
the colors that'll

00:17:20.280 --> 00:17:23.410
flow through the app,
styling both the MDC Android

00:17:23.410 --> 00:17:26.440
components, but also lower
level UI elements provided

00:17:26.440 --> 00:17:29.640
by the Android framework.

