00:18:04.820 --> 00:18:07.160
to use Work Sans with
a light text style.

00:18:09.700 --> 00:18:11.650
We can redefine the
entire type scale

00:18:11.650 --> 00:18:13.390
and link it up
through our theme so

00:18:13.390 --> 00:18:15.910
that all of the text appearances
update across your app.

00:18:18.812 --> 00:18:20.270
So with those
changes to our theme,

00:18:20.270 --> 00:18:22.910
we see Reply's colors
and typography permeate

00:18:22.910 --> 00:18:26.100
through the components and
the various views of the app.

