00:19:59.260 --> 00:20:00.880
The tonal color
palette that we use

00:20:00.880 --> 00:20:04.110
has fairly minimal
contrast in this case.

00:20:04.110 --> 00:20:06.370
OK, those are really key
choices because think

00:20:06.370 --> 00:20:10.049
about what a user coming to
this experience was looking for.

00:20:10.049 --> 00:20:11.590
They want to engage
with the content.

00:20:11.590 --> 00:20:14.350
They want to be excited
by the different wares

00:20:14.350 --> 00:20:16.270
that you have up
for sale and keep

00:20:16.270 --> 00:20:18.250
their attention focused there.

00:20:18.250 --> 00:20:22.280
But you also need to be
able to convert them.

00:20:22.280 --> 00:20:24.820
They need to be able to
find that add to cart button

00:20:24.820 --> 00:20:27.710
and hit it when it's time for
