00:20:36.420 --> 00:20:38.010
actually recedes a little bit.

00:20:38.010 --> 00:20:41.290
Content and key
actions go forward.

00:20:41.290 --> 00:20:45.110
Where shrine does assert its
brand identity very strongly

00:20:45.110 --> 00:20:48.740
is in the way that
