But we aim at making
adjusting shape

00:22:33.299 --> 00:22:34.840
and applying it to
your components as

00:22:34.840 --> 00:22:38.410
simple as theming any other
aspect of your design.

00:22:38.410 --> 00:22:41.800
Here for Shrine we use this cut
on the corners of the buttons

00:22:41.800 --> 00:22:45.870
