00:23:24.931 --> 00:23:26.430
With that, hopefully
I've gotten you

00:23:26.430 --> 00:23:28.890
excited about material
components, the benefits they

00:23:28.890 --> 00:23:31.320
provide, and the ease in
which they enable these very

00:23:31.320 --> 00:23:33.252
sophisticated customizations.

